name: Vladimir Makhaev
title: Senior Software Developer
intro:
Have good experience in back-end mostly Golang and NodeJS, but can write number of other languages, like Lua, C#, C, Python, Rust looks promising, at some point it does not matter, you know. Databases mostly Mongo, Redis, Rabbit, but have played with number of others, like Postgres, Tarantool, Elastic Search, Clickhouse, Hadoop/Spark, Nats, Mysql, Sql Server, etc. Have experience of Devops Teamlead with estabilishing CI/CD for microservices and deep dive into Kubernetes. Worked with all major cloud providers: GCP, AWS, Azure and DIgital Ocean. Also have good experience with front-end (React and number of other frameworks) and React Native for mobile development.
